{"tid":1119964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他們曾說過……","createTime":"2019-04-22T10:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T10:05:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b676c6332e3250801cd03fe942463839304a60dd","tid":1119964,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:05:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190422/20661373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190422%2F20661373&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6jvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=9c880762\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190422%2F20661373&h=ebf34b57\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190422/20661373</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他們曾說過&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190422/large/a0902a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190422%2Flarge%2Fa0902a.gif&h=23edea74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔣彥永<br />\n<br />\n「當局希望人們會漸漸淡忘：過去把天安門事件稱作『反革命暴亂』，後來就改稱為『89年的政治風波』。這種對事件名稱的更改，正說明肇事者的心虛。既然是風波，何以要動用數十萬軍隊去鎮壓？怎麼能用機槍坦克去殘殺無辜的百姓？所以我建議，要為89年六四學生愛國運動正名。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黎智英：平反靠希望<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曾揭露中國政府隱瞞沙士疫情的<br />\n北京301醫院退休軍醫蔣彥永，2004年上書中央領導  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n黎智英：平反靠希望<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n蘋人誌︰ 風流自在 女同志烏托邦<br />\n<br />\n黎智英：平反靠希望"}]}